{"tid":2514000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"洪水橋真槍案 銷售員涉藏槍及390發子彈 押後至月尾再進行交付高等法院程序","createTime":"2021-05-03T03:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T03:42:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e3bdd7e9d9e9f352accdea7264a4435f24e74ae5","tid":2514000,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:30:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15386&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=c7f6c14f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15386</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#鄧少雄裁判官<br />\n#20200609元朗<br />\n#提訊日<br />\n<br />\n陳(38) 🛑已還押逾11個月<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n意圖危害生命而管有槍械或彈藥 [第238章《火器及彈藥條例》16(1)及(2)]<br />\n<br />\n控罪詳情：<br />\n2020年6月9日在元朗洪水橋石埗村403號富𧙗居B座地下，管有一支設計作可發射9x19毫米口徑子彈的手槍及390發9x19毫米口徑子彈及4個彈匣而無持有該等槍械及彈藥的管有權牌照，意圖危害生命。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n📌辯方表示可答辯但控方通知將修訂控罪(庭上沒有讀出)，要求押後四星期再作提訊<br />\n<br />\n📌案件將押後至 5月31日 1130 於東區裁判法院第七庭進行交付高等法院審訊程序。<br />\n<br />\n被告沒有保釋申請，繼續還押 ‼️<br />\n（按：手足庭上有和親友及旁聽人士揮手，精神唔錯)"},{"pid":"27cf0d207d8acf677f0567e36d19431a86a4062f","tid":2514000,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"又押後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca534244755174b2314cbe1c5f8879cec56ead56","tid":2514000,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117c75fd78147191988e60b4bf4cfba2d11e61f0","tid":2514000,"uid":52705,"like":0,"disli